divs: Sighting DetailsWe were driving east on buttercup lane when my daughter saw two bright lights in the sky. We both looked up and we saw something that looked like a V. It had two bright lights at each end, and a center light that was green. It was coming toward us then it turned towards the southwest. We tried to follow it to get a better look and as we turned it disappeared.
